data.description: Charming home in Kalispell on a roomy corner lot offering the perfect blend of comfort, convenience and potential. Featuring: 2 Bedrooms, 1 Full Bathroom, spacious kitchen & living room, dining area and home office nook. Remodeled in 2017 (including new flooring, new kitchen and bathroom). Quick and easy access to restaurants, nearby grocery stores, close to downtown. Main floor: 1,117 sq. ft., Basement: 448 sq. ft., zoned R-1, Detached Garage. Plenty of room to park your boat, RV, etc. No Covenants or HOA. This property offers endless possibilities with its functional layout and versatile zoning. Enjoy the fruit trees in early autumn, currently loaded with purple plums and apples! Transform the unfinished basement into a hobby room or home gym. This central location ensures you're just moments away from all the services and events that Kalispell has to offer. Call Mike 406.871.0673 or Shelby 406.253.0222 or your real estate professional today!
